  Key design decisions:                                                                                                                    
  - Home page reads from Supabase (fast) — sync is triggered manually via the button, not on every load
  - getMarkets() paginates via next_cursor and caps at 500 to prevent hanging syncs                                                          
  - Combined price column already flags arb opportunities in green with an ARB badge — useful for Phase 2